      • existsAsType

        public static boolean existsAsType(String nameOrId)
        Checks whether entity exists in KB and is an instance of #$Individual. If false, getStatus(String) may yield more information. This method is equivalent to getStatus(nameOrId).equals(KBStatus.EXISTS_AS_TYPE).
        Parameters:
        nameOrId - either the name or HL ID of an entity in the KB
        Returns:
        true if entity exists in KB and is an instance of #$Individual
